[[File:XC3 Lucky Enemy.jpeg|thumb|A Lucky Feris]] '''Lucky Monsters''' (Japanese: {{Lang|jp|ラッキーモンスター}}, ''rakkīmonsutā'') are [[Enemy (XC3)|enemies]] in {{XC3}}. They are as strong as normal monsters, but provide better items upon defeat. [[File:XC3 Fairscale Marina.png|thumb|An example of a Lucky Unique Monster.]] [[Elite Monster|Elite]] and [[Unique Monster (XC3)|Unique Monsters]] can also be Lucky Monsters as well.
The probability of encountering a Lucky Monster is affected by the Shiny Hunter Affinity Bonus, which increases the odds by 1-10%.
{{clr}}
