{{Infobox item |name = Noponic Gold |image = XC3 key item.png |caption = "Unlocks Lucky Seven in the Archsage's Gauntlet Hard mode." |type = Key Item |xc3rarity = Legendary |source = [[Prize X-change Blue]] |sell = N/A }} The '''Lucky Seven License''' is a DLC [[Key Item]] in {{XC3}}. It can be bought from the [[Prize X-change Blue]] for 60,000 blue [[Noponstone]]. It allows [[Noah]] to use [[Infinity Blade (XC3)|Infinity Blade]] and [[Unlimited Sword]] as his Talent Art on the hard [[Difficulty Levels|difficulty]] during the [[Archsage's Gauntlet]]. {{clr}}
